    <item>
      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0160回】 嚴格的技法</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0101-0200/t-0160-strict-aiki-way/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Feb 2026 23:50:54 +0800</pubDate>
